viewdefs.DNASequence:
<viewdef name="DNASequence" type="form" class="edu.ku.brc.specify.datamodel.DNASequence" gettable="edu.ku.brc.af.ui.forms.DataGetterForObj" settable="edu.ku.brc.af.ui.forms.DataSetterForObj">
            <desc>DNA Sequence Form</desc>
            <enableRules />

            <columnDef>100px,2px,76px,2px,100px,5px,108px,2px,130px,5px,100px,2px,195px,0px,15px,p:g</columnDef>
            <columnDef os="lnx">115px,2px,66px,2px,113px,2px,140px,2px,133px,5px,125px,2px,210px,0px,15px,p:g</columnDef>
            <columnDef os="mac">130px,2px,86px,2px,123px,2px,340px,2px,93px,5px,105px,2px,230px,0px,15px,p:g</columnDef>
            <columnDef os="exp">p,2px,p:g,2px,p:g(2),5px,p:g,2px,p:g(2),5px:g,p,2px,p:g,0px,p,p:g</columnDef>
            <rowDef auto="true" cell="p" sep="2px" />

            <rows>
                <row>
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="11" />
                    <cell type="field" id="11" name="boldBarcodeId" uitype="text" />
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="2" />
                    <cell type="field" id="2" name="moleculeType" uitype="combobox" colspan="3" />
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="22" />
                    <cell type="field" id="22" name="sequencer" uitype="querycbx" initialize="name=Agent" colspan="3" />
                </row>
				<row>
                    <cell type="field" id="WebLink2" name="text2" uitype="plugin" initialize="name=WebLinkButton;weblink=Genbank" colspan="3" />
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="55" />
                    <cell type="field" id="55" name="text1" uitype="text" colspan="7" />
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell type="separator" label="Nucleotide Sequence" colspan="15" />
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell type="panel" id="16" name="outerPanel" coldef="100px,2px,76px" rowdef="p,2px,p,2px,p,2px,p,2px,p,2px,p,2px" colspan="3">
                      <rows>
	                      <row>
	                          <cell type="label" label="Total Residues:" initialize="align=right" />
	                          <cell type="field" id="residues" name="totalResidues" uitype="text" readonly="true" />
	                      </row>
	                      <row>
	                          <cell type="label" label="Comp A:" initialize="align=right;fg=0,190,0" />
	                          <cell type="field" id="compA" name="compA" uitype="text" readonly="true" />
	                      </row>
	                      <row>
	                          <cell type="label" label="Comp G:" initialize="align=right;fg=200,70,0" />
	                          <cell type="field" id="compG" name="compG" uitype="text" readonly="true" />
	                      </row>
	                      <row>
	                          <cell type="label" label="Comp C:" initialize="align=right;fg=0,0,190" />
	                          <cell type="field" id="compC" name="compC" uitype="text" readonly="true" />
	                      </row>
	                      <row>
	                          <cell type="label" label="Comp T:" initialize="align=right;fg=190,0,0" />
	                          <cell type="field" id="compT" name="compT" uitype="text" readonly="true" />
	                      </row>
	                      <row>
	                          <cell type="label" label="Ambiguous:" initialize="align=right" />
	                          <cell type="field" id="ambiguous" name="ambiguousResidues" uitype="text" readonly="true" />
	                      </row>
	                  </rows>
	              </cell>
                    <cell type="label" labelfor="4" />
                    <cell type="field" id="4" name="geneSequence" uitype="textareabrief" colspan="8" rows="10" />
	              </row>
                  
                
                
            </rows>
        </viewdef>
